        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>No 22<del><hi rend="sup">nd</hi></del> 8 Street</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">care of <persName>Mr Keiler</persName></p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>St. Louis</placeName>
                <date>7 May 5625</date>.</p>
            <p>Dr Sir.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I take myself the honor,<lb/> in dropping these few lines<lb/> to
                thank you for the aquain-<lb/><sic>tance</sic> &amp; the kindness shown<lb/> to me
                at my calling on you<lb/> last <date><sic>wednesday</sic></date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Just at my arrival here<lb/> a <persName>Mr Moses</persName> with
                eight<lb/> singers was appointed to read<lb/> last <add>שבת</add>, I therefore shall
                do so<lb/> next <add>שבת</add> &amp; stopping with the above<lb/> gentleman the
                treasurer of <add>קהילה</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">If I remain here for longer<lb/> I do not know</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I forgot at the <placeName>market<lb/> Str</placeName> Hotel my pink
                silk hank<lb/><sic>erchief</sic> &amp; do not know to write to<lb/> him. My name is
                booked there<lb/> &amp; I should be glad if you will be kind<lb/> enough to take
                posse<lb/>sion of it, until I see<lb/> you again pl. God</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Abr. Goldschmidt</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Dr Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
